      "summary": "Arshad Zackeriya (Zack) is a Platform Engineer and an AWS Hero 🦸‍♂️ , based in Wellington, New Zealand 🇳🇿 🥝. As a voice in the AWS cloud community, he serves as the AWS User Group Leader for Wellington, New Zealand. Zack is specializes in AWS Cloud, Linux, and Kubernetes, sharing his expertise as a prolific blogger, podcaster, and mentor. When not architecting cloud solutions, he enjoys swimming, cooking, and collecting Lego Technics",
